{t:IT'S A LOVELY, LOVELY NAME #012}
{st:}
012 G

It's a lovely, lovely, Name,
The Name of Jesus.
It's a lovely, lovely, Name
From heaven above.
Dispelling the clouds of doubt and
fear,
Filling the saddened heart with
cheer,
It's a lovely, lovely, Name
The Name I love.




